              <div class="box ">
                <div class="img-box">
                  <img src="images/average.png" alt="" />
                </div>
                <div class="detail-box">
                  <h5>
                    Average
                  </h5>
                  <p>
                    Average denotes a middle point. In various contexts, it signifies typical performance, quality, or quantity, serving as a benchmark for comparison.
